u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 k\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c nhau. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch <\/span>thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t chung c\u01b0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft b\u1ea1n n\u00ean \u0111i theo \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0o, h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 Byzan g\u1ee3i \u00fd nh\u1eefng<\/span> m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho ch\u00ednh ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3305\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/thiet-ke-noi-that-phong-ngu-30.jpg\" alt=\"thiet-ke-noi-that-phong-ngu\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/thiet-ke-noi-that-phong-ngu-30.jpg 2000w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/thiet-ke-noi-that-phong-ngu-30-300x210.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/thiet-ke-noi-that-phong-ngu-30-768x538.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/thiet-ke-noi-that-phong-ngu-30-1024x717.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" \/>1. Nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc <\/span>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 Phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3310\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/thiet-ke-noi-that-phong-ngu-24.jpg\" alt=\"thiet-ke-noi-that-phong-ngu\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/thiet-ke-noi-that-phong-ngu-24.jpg 2000w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01